These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, rat, chinchilla
There 4 different types of food: peach, pepper, pomegranate, nectarine
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the far left##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is between the person eating pepper and the owner of the horse##2
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the hedgehog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Pet   | chinchilla         | horse   | rat | hedgehog       |
| Food      | nectarine | peach | pomegranate   | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, scrabble, backgammon
4 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, horse, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person playing scrabble and the owner of the goldfish##2
2. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | monopoly | billiard | scrabble | backgammon |
| Pet   | goldfish    | guinea-pig   | dog | horse       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bongani, siglo, prince
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, motorbike, helicopter
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the bus and the bongani-smoker##2
3. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the bongani-smoker is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar          | prince    | dunhill | bongani   | siglo  |
| Transport   | bus | motorbike   | helicopter | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, canadian, japanese, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, salsa, house, r&b
1. the fan salsa is the canadian##1
2. the egyptian is between the fan techno and the brazilian##2
3. the fan salsa is on the far right##1
4. the egyptian is on the right of the fan house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality     | brazilian   | egyptian    | japanese       | canadian   |
| Music-Genre   | house | r&b | techno | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, basketball, tennis, rowing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, ambient, punk, techno
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the fan punk is on the far left##1
3. the fan jazz is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the fan jazz and the fan ambient##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Sport   | soccer        | tennis | rowing  | basketball |
| Music-Genre      | punk | ambient  | techno | jazz    |

