.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
City: london, miami, marseilles, prague
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, time-travel, comedy, disaster
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person traveling to prague is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to miami is the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to miami##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| City   | miami     | marseilles           | london | prague  |
| Movie-Genre         | spy | disaster | time-travel   | comedy |

