.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, bird, mouse, dog
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, july, may, november
1. the owner of the bird is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the owner of the pony is between the person who's birthday is in february and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet   | dog   | bird | pony | mouse      |
| Birthday     | may | february    | july  | november |

