.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, country, techno, rock
City: hannover, paris, liverpool, london
1. the person traveling to hannover is the fan country##1
2. the person traveling to paris is between the fan techno and the person traveling to liverpool##2
3. the fan d&b is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre       | d&b | rock | techno     | country   |
| City   | liverpool   | paris     | london | hannover |

