.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
City: london, boston, hannover, hamburg
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, cola, sprite
1. the person traveling to hannover is between the person drinking lemonade and the person traveling to london##2
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| City         | boston | hannover | london | hamburg |
| Beverage   | lemonade         | sprite       | iced-tea    | cola         |

