.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, german, mexican
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, iced-tea, coffee
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the mexican##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the german##1
3. the australian is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking juice is between the canadian and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality    | mexican   | german      | canadian   | australian  |
| Beverage   | coffee | juice | iced-tea | sprite |

