3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| City          | berlin     | paris | nizza   | prague        |
| Flower   | poppy | iris   | aconite | tulip |

