.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, volleyball, soccer
There 4 different types of food: apricot, peas, peach, cranberry
1. the person eating peach is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
3. the person eating apricot is the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person eating peas is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | soccer | climbing |
| Food   | peach          | peas     | cranberry  | apricot     |

