.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, mango, eggplant, pepper
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, skateboard, bike, trike
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating pepper is between the person driving the trike and the person eating garlic##2
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
4. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Food           | garlic | pepper | mango | eggplant     |
| Transport   | snowmobile   | bike    | trike   | skateboard |

