There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, almond-milk, cola
1. the montecristo-smoker is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Cigar           | bluemaster | oliveros | game | montecristo |
| Beverage   | fanta   | milk | cola         | almond-milk |

