.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
House: wooden, modern, colonial, cape-cod
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis, rose, orchid
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the cape-cod house is between the person who growsorchid and the wooden house##2
3. the modern house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| House         | wooden      | cape-cod | modern  | colonial |
| Flower   | amaryllis | rose  | orchid | bellflower    |

