.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: french, mexican, chinese, dutch
1. the mexican is on the right of the french##1
2. the french is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the french and the person drinking mirinda##2
4. the person drinking sprite is the french##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage       | sprite | hot-chocolate | mirinda | 7up |
| Nationality   | french    | mexican  | dutch    | chinese       |

