.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, september, july
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, balloon-flower, iris
1. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsiris is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in september##2
5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | july   | december   | february | september |
| Flower         | dahlia | sunflower | iris     | balloon-flower    |

