.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, scrabble, whist
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, october, march
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
2. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person playing whist##2
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Game   | scrabble    | whist     | backgammon | poker |
| Birthday     | may | march | october       | april     |

 